  "detailed_description": "Into the Dread is a survival horror game inspired by the PSX era. You decided that exploring an abandoned sewer would be fun. Of course, something went wrong, and you were trapped in it. <br><br>Explore the sewer, find various supplies and deal with the terrifying monsters in it.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054960/extras/0f7b32961c7bc6376b9a7bef638d6edf.poster.avif?t=1737533955\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054960/extras/0f7b32961c7bc6376b9a7bef638d6edf.webm?t=1737533955\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054960/extras/0f7b32961c7bc6376b9a7bef638d6edf.mp4?t=1737533955\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Setting inspired by PSX era.<br></li><li>Survival Horror inspired by iconic games.<br></li><li>Solve puzzles to progress through the story.<br></li><li>Bloody and abandoned environment.<br></li><li>A variety of firearms.<br></li><li>Enemy design inspired by nightmares.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3054960/extras/5e40539547b19a5bed6e424215ae03ac.avif?t=1737533955\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br><br>Something is clearly wrong with this place! Will you be able to escape from this nightmare and kill everyone standing in your way?",
